summary: hi friends!! I really need help from somebody who has a VIP for interactive introverts!! so dan and phil have done so much for...
body:
INTERACTIVE INTROVERTS HELP PLEASE

hi friends!! I really need help from somebody who has a VIP for interactive introverts!! so dan and phil have done so much for me in my life and helped me through the absolute darkest of times. throughout all the super dark times, dan’s quote “embrace the void and have the courage to exist” has kept me going more than i can even express. so to thank them for all they’ve done and to help me never forget what they’ve done, I want to get the phrase “have the courage to exist” written in Dan and Phil’s handwriting for the longest time. so would anybody going to VIP for any of the shows be willing to ask phil to write out “have the courage” and dan to write out “to exist” for me just like the photo below please???? I will literally do anything to have somebody do this for me friends pls spread the word or message me if you are willing to help me it would mean the absolute world to me!!! thank you!!
